<li><a href="https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/e/2PACX-1vRotONrAXoAu1zRxf_yWVzvTN4I_fZ_5WmrC3wf6jZ0q-3GH7ZqMBoq65JTZC5xBWBiKOKstNtAq_QI/pub?start=false&amp;loop=false&amp;delayms=3000">Connecting an iPad to Home WiFi</a></li>
